WEBVTT

00:00.024 --> 00:04.972
♪ Hey, why is it happening ♪

00:05.944 --> 00:08.652
♪ My heart is racing ♪

00:09.784 --> 00:13.792
♪ The world has fallen silent ♪

00:13.816 --> 00:18.572
♪ Hey, when I imagine you ♪

00:19.608 --> 00:22.636
♪ What kind of look ♪

00:23.640 --> 00:27.584
♪ Attracted me to you ♪

00:27.608 --> 00:30.880
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:30.904 --> 00:34.368
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:34.392 --> 00:39.640
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:39.640 --> 00:41.258
♪ I love you ♪

00:41.258 --> 00:44.736
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:44.760 --> 00:48.032
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:48.056 --> 00:53.728
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:53.752 --> 00:55.096
♪ I love you ♪

00:55.096 --> 00:58.432
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:58.456 --> 01:01.804
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:01.912 --> 01:07.109
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:07.109 --> 01:08.792
♪ I love you ♪

01:08.792 --> 01:12.192
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

01:12.216 --> 01:15.616
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:15.640 --> 01:21.216
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:21.240 --> 01:24.652
♪ I love you ♪

01:26.930 --> 01:27.720
=Love Me, Love My Voice=

01:27.720 --> 01:30.754
=Love Me, Love My Voice=
=Episode 33=

01:30.754 --> 01:35.193
(If you don't mind, we'll take
the wedding photos here.)

01:35.756 --> 01:37.891
Sir, madam,
where should I put your suitcase?

01:37.915 --> 01:39.036
- Put it there. Thanks.
- Okay.

01:39.036 --> 01:40.296
Give it to me.

01:40.956 --> 01:42.415
Call me if you're in need.

01:42.876 --> 01:46.932
- Then I'll put it inside.
- Mr. Mo, as you asked,

01:46.956 --> 01:50.811
I've had the girl's clothes ironed.
Your suit will be delivered shortly.

01:50.835 --> 01:54.016
- Thank you.
- Wishing you a happy wedding.

02:05.596 --> 02:06.695
Have a look.

02:34.195 --> 02:35.616
The view of Guilin is good.

02:36.355 --> 02:37.656
If you don't mind,

02:39.036 --> 02:40.776
we'll take the wedding photos here.

02:47.395 --> 02:49.216
It took quite a long time to choose.

02:50.116 --> 02:51.936
I asked your best friends around you.

02:52.556 --> 02:54.135
Based on everyone's opinions.

02:57.955 --> 02:59.465
No need to be too nervous.

02:59.465 --> 03:03.216
This isn't a wedding dress.
It's just for taking pictures.

03:03.795 --> 03:07.376
As for the formal dress,
you'll choose it yourself.

03:10.395 --> 03:13.616
And I especially chose today.

03:14.355 --> 03:16.256
It's memorable for you.

03:19.276 --> 03:20.376
Happy graduation.

03:36.276 --> 03:37.496
But

03:39.716 --> 03:43.536
I'm too shy to take pictures
in front of so many people,

03:44.075 --> 03:45.575
especially of this kind.

03:49.036 --> 03:50.256
They don't know.

03:51.756 --> 03:52.895
They don't know?

03:54.716 --> 03:56.175
Thinking you'd feel uneasy,

03:56.716 --> 03:59.176
I just told them I wanted
to pick out a formal dress for you

03:59.176 --> 04:01.695
and didn't mention
this outdoor shoot in Yangshuo.

04:06.635 --> 04:07.816
Then we...

04:08.996 --> 04:10.095
Secretly.

04:27.916 --> 04:30.296
- Still the same.
- Right.

04:33.515 --> 04:35.955
- You two finally arrived.
- Long time no see.

04:35.955 --> 04:38.852
I've been by the water all afternoon,
just watching the sun.

04:38.876 --> 04:41.772
I was afraid it would set too soon
and it'd miss your shoot.

04:41.796 --> 04:43.316
Your boyfriend has really good taste,

04:43.316 --> 04:45.976
choosing Yangshuo as the place
for the wedding photos.

04:46.116 --> 04:47.931
- Thank you.
- You're welcome.

04:47.955 --> 04:50.805
I love any happy occasion,
sharing happiness.

04:50.805 --> 04:52.015
Mr. Qiang.

04:52.876 --> 04:55.835
- You're here.
- Those two say they are your friends.

04:55.835 --> 04:56.976
Yes, they are.

04:58.035 --> 04:59.335
Do you remember me?

05:04.676 --> 05:07.131
You were the photographer
on the 10th anniversary two years ago.

05:07.155 --> 05:10.732
You remember me. I didn't
come all the way from downtown in vain.

05:10.756 --> 05:13.936
- I'll leave you guys to chat.
- Okay.

05:14.556 --> 05:16.691
As for me, I'm a stranger to you.

05:16.715 --> 05:18.652
A nobody in the Perfect Voice Studio
in the past.

05:18.676 --> 05:21.376
- I'll do your makeup styling today.
- Hello.

05:23.075 --> 05:27.455
- I finally held Mr. Qiang's girlfriend.
- Be reserved.

05:27.515 --> 05:30.131
You don't understand. It is the feeling
of a club veteran for Mr. Qiang.

05:30.155 --> 05:33.275
Seeing his girlfriend made me happy
from the bottom of my heart.

05:33.275 --> 05:36.412
Alright, make the most of the time.
Let's finish shooting before dark.

05:36.436 --> 05:38.532
Half an hour for makeup
and hair styling, okay?

05:38.556 --> 05:40.892
- A piece of cake.
- Then let's go upstairs.

05:40.916 --> 05:42.275
- Okay.
- Let's go. This way.

05:42.275 --> 05:43.736
Okay. Let's go.

05:45.635 --> 05:46.695
Over there.

05:48.876 --> 05:49.895
Come.

05:56.835 --> 05:58.075
The lady just now

05:58.075 --> 06:01.736
specially cleared this room for you
to do makeup. Go ahead and start.

06:02.195 --> 06:04.775
- Sit.
- Come.

06:05.316 --> 06:08.732
Enjoy the view, scroll
through your phone, fill up your cart

06:08.756 --> 06:10.575
and let Mr. Qiang pay for the items.

06:13.635 --> 06:16.056
Then you go ahead. I'll go downstairs.

06:22.476 --> 06:25.655
- Worrying that he'll run away?
- No.

06:26.075 --> 06:28.744
I remember you were in college
when he pursued you, right?

06:28.744 --> 06:30.332
Senior year.

06:30.356 --> 06:33.532
- And now, where are you working?
- I officially graduated today.

06:33.556 --> 06:35.732
I just attended
the grad school ceremony.

06:35.756 --> 06:38.748
You flew here right
after the ceremony this morning?

06:39.144 --> 06:41.655
Graduation photos in the morning
and wedding photos in the afternoon.

06:42.635 --> 06:43.816
That's awesome.

06:44.436 --> 06:47.895
I didn't expect this.
It is a surprise for me.

08:21.246 --> 08:24.999
♪ Where should I start
about millions of dawns and dusks ♪

08:24.999 --> 08:27.207
♪ Depict a stroke
of rain before the mountain ♪

08:27.207 --> 08:29.606
♪ Stars beyond the sky ♪

08:29.630 --> 08:33.735
♪ Bit by bit, it outlines
yesterday and today ♪

08:33.735 --> 08:36.295
♪ And you with
picturesque eyebrows and eyes ♪

08:36.295 --> 08:38.779
♪ Jointly create the mood ♪

08:39.838 --> 08:43.559
♪ The rain and fog
over the mountains are intriguing ♪

08:43.559 --> 08:44.967
♪ It seems I can't get enough of seeing ♪

08:44.967 --> 08:48.056
♪ The once inexhaustible journey ♪

08:48.056 --> 08:49.095
♪ On this journey ♪

08:49.095 --> 08:50.791
♪ The stars accompany me
along thousands of miles ♪

08:50.791 --> 08:52.966
♪ I walk down with you ♪

08:52.966 --> 08:57.627
♪ Spending dawns and dusks together
for a hundred years ♪

08:57.694 --> 08:59.591
♪ Just like ♪

08:59.591 --> 09:00.521
♪ When the clouds are low ♪

09:00.521 --> 09:02.146
♪ It rains ♪

09:02.146 --> 09:06.610
♪ I was moved
when you were singing softly ♪

09:06.610 --> 09:10.343
♪ Since then, I hear stars every night ♪

09:10.343 --> 09:11.431
♪ And rains at midnight ♪

09:11.431 --> 09:15.904
♪ I could hear you
among millions of voices ♪

09:15.904 --> 09:18.379
♪ All other voices fade away ♪

09:18.379 --> 09:20.785
♪ I hear your monologue ♪

09:20.785 --> 09:25.145
♪ Saying I miss you so much ♪

09:25.145 --> 09:27.591
♪ Like knowing the implied meaning
of a picture ♪

09:27.591 --> 09:30.723
♪ Knowing your happiness and sadness ♪

09:31.356 --> 09:35.420
You're dressed differently today
from you usually are on stage.

09:36.853 --> 09:39.454
♪ I hear your voice ♪

09:39.454 --> 09:42.694
♪ Saying I miss you so much ♪

09:42.718 --> 09:44.163
It is special today.

09:46.043 --> 09:48.570
♪ Kisses like pouring rain ♪

09:48.570 --> 09:52.231
♪ Lightly falling
outside and inside the dream ♪

09:52.235 --> 09:56.204
♪ With you in this life ♪

09:59.596 --> 10:02.535
Good. Look at me. Smile.

10:05.116 --> 10:06.696
Look at the groom.

10:10.915 --> 10:14.251
Smile. Lady, look at me.

10:14.275 --> 10:18.295
Look at me. Be more natural. Smile.

10:19.196 --> 10:20.976
Smile happily.

10:22.476 --> 10:25.376
Look at me. Good.

10:26.435 --> 10:29.736
Golden Piglet,
are you forced to marry him?

10:31.996 --> 10:35.131
Be happier. You are taking
outdoor wedding photos.

10:35.155 --> 10:39.216
- With green mountains as the backdrop.
- I'm not unhappy.

10:39.716 --> 10:41.775
I just lack experience.

10:44.196 --> 10:46.972
What are you doing?
You scared me to death.

10:46.996 --> 10:49.256
If you don't laugh, I'll pick you up.

10:50.476 --> 10:52.295
One, two.

10:53.116 --> 10:57.015
No. The boat will really capsize
if you do this.

10:57.756 --> 10:59.295
Okay, this is nice.

11:01.196 --> 11:03.535
Keep going.

11:05.716 --> 11:08.696
Very good. So beautiful.

11:11.155 --> 11:18.576
- Keep it up.
- Does anyone want to see a kiss? Kiss.

11:19.675 --> 11:23.055
- In broad daylight?
- And it's outdoors.

11:24.435 --> 11:27.411
No, no way.

11:27.435 --> 11:30.336
- You'd fall into the water.
- The water isn't deep anyway.

11:30.476 --> 11:32.866
Right, we can shoot
some behind-the-scenes.

11:32.866 --> 11:35.208
Lots of good photos
were shot in the water.

11:35.208 --> 11:37.572
Mr. Qiang, you're in a suit.

11:37.596 --> 11:40.336
Get in the water,
and your erotic appeal will come out.

11:40.395 --> 11:43.915
Agree, Mr. Qiang. Sheng wants to see it.

11:43.915 --> 11:47.576
It's summer and we've been shooting
for so long. Aren't you hot?

11:47.795 --> 11:51.092
Getting into the water to cool off.
Come on. How nice it will be!

11:51.116 --> 11:54.332
This is Yangshuo in Guilin.
A once-in-a-lifetime opportunity.

11:54.356 --> 11:57.376
- It's a lot more fun than the seaside.
- Exactly.

12:05.395 --> 12:06.976
Look at them.

12:07.635 --> 12:09.135
Be reserved.

12:10.956 --> 12:12.411
I can't suppress it anymore.

12:12.435 --> 12:14.976
- Just a moment. Do it fast.
- Okay.

12:15.035 --> 12:16.496
Into the water.

12:21.836 --> 12:25.616
- No, I won't go down.
- How are we gonna shoot if you don't?

12:25.716 --> 12:27.376
I really won't go down.

12:27.956 --> 12:29.376
I'll carry you onshore.

12:33.395 --> 12:35.216
I really...

12:35.956 --> 12:39.212
- No. Put me down!
- Don't move. I'll take you onshore.

12:39.236 --> 12:40.812
- No, put me down!
- Don't move.

12:40.836 --> 12:43.295
- Put me down!
- You're gonna fall in the water.

12:43.435 --> 12:47.256
- But my veil will get wet.
- It belongs to you already.

13:12.116 --> 13:13.795
- Look at me.
- We'll take a lot of photos.

13:13.795 --> 13:15.356
- Yes, it's really good.
- So happy.

13:15.356 --> 13:19.696
- Go forward. It's really good.
- So envious.

13:21.515 --> 13:22.696
Satisfied now?

13:23.675 --> 13:25.616
Yes, very much so.

13:37.555 --> 13:41.135
How come we encounter such a good thing?

13:41.956 --> 13:43.736
This is a hidden Easter egg.

13:44.596 --> 13:46.055
Really happy.

13:47.675 --> 13:51.152
- Why are you so happy?
- Qiang Qingci is a man.

13:51.176 --> 13:52.915
His love story has come to fruition.

13:52.915 --> 13:57.336
Come look this way.
Mr. Qiang, smile. Right.

13:57.596 --> 14:01.696
Super handsome.
Golden Piglet, hug him. Right.

14:01.996 --> 14:03.275
So beautiful.

14:03.275 --> 14:06.692
If we go now, can we still catch up
with Sheng shooting on the shore?

14:06.716 --> 14:09.216
Get closer. Good.

14:11.515 --> 14:15.616
Sheng is shy.
If we go now, she'll act unnatural.

14:26.756 --> 14:28.055
Really happy.

14:34.515 --> 14:36.096
So you can smile.

14:53.756 --> 14:56.336
What a pity for your suit.

14:57.116 --> 15:00.015
Not getting in the water yourself
but urging me.

15:00.315 --> 15:02.935
Not having even a bit of guilt
and still laughing.

15:03.476 --> 15:05.535
But the photos are very good.

15:06.315 --> 15:10.616
- As long as you think they're good.
- Aren't they? They're really beautiful.

15:13.515 --> 15:14.596
I got so mad at the time.

15:14.596 --> 15:18.055
As soon as I saw her, a pretty girl,
I knelt down right away.

15:19.236 --> 15:20.596
- Was it successful?
- So chill.

15:20.596 --> 15:22.935
- Really?
- It was many years ago.

15:25.315 --> 15:30.096
Where did you two go just now?
How did you get here earlier than us?

15:31.356 --> 15:35.376
- We've just arrived too.
- Let's go. Don't disturb them.

15:35.596 --> 15:38.395
- Let's go.
- You guys keep staring.

15:38.395 --> 15:40.065
What about the wedding dress?

15:40.065 --> 15:43.376
I agreed with the owner
to pack it up later tonight.

15:46.236 --> 15:47.456
Let's go downstairs.

15:48.236 --> 15:51.015
Come on in. Sit anywhere at this table.

15:51.515 --> 15:54.856
We've prepared oil tea for everyone.
You can drink it.

15:55.076 --> 15:58.531
- Mr. Zhu has got into someone again.
- Looking forward to coming here.

15:58.555 --> 16:02.775
My apologies first.
Tonight, there will be only fish dishes.

16:03.315 --> 16:06.172
- Please forgive us.
- Is there nothing else except fish?

16:06.196 --> 16:07.815
There's also oil tea.

16:12.315 --> 16:15.496
What a big restaurant
and you only have one dish?

16:15.795 --> 16:17.655
And it isn't closed yet?

16:18.716 --> 16:20.216
That's really something.

16:21.555 --> 16:25.172
- Deliberate cliffhanger.
- Sorry.

16:25.196 --> 16:27.172
- He's like this.
- Shut up, okay?

16:27.196 --> 16:29.996
- The fish dishes here are different.
- What's the difference?

16:29.996 --> 16:34.815
- What is it?
- Actually, we have other dishes here,

16:34.876 --> 16:39.052
but today, I specially invited a chef.

16:39.076 --> 16:43.736
I asked him to cook ten dishes
with the fish from the Lijiang River.

16:46.716 --> 16:48.015
So that's how it is.

16:48.515 --> 16:51.256
- So it's Chef Mo.
- It's you.

16:51.756 --> 16:55.172
The kitchen is ready, and the fish
were all freshly caught today.

16:55.196 --> 16:57.615
- Okay, thank you.
- You're welcome.

16:58.835 --> 17:02.136
Mo's fish dishes are second
to none in the world.

17:02.595 --> 17:05.051
- They're good.
- Thank you, Mr. Qiang.

17:05.075 --> 17:08.476
He told me that his cooking skills
were quite good. It's true?

17:08.476 --> 17:09.212
- Yes.
- True.

17:09.236 --> 17:14.011
- That's more than just good.
- How did you convince him to cook?

17:14.035 --> 17:15.905
It's usually quite difficult to

17:15.905 --> 17:17.412
- get him into the kitchen.
- Indeed.

17:17.436 --> 17:22.456
I didn't trick him.
He insisted on cooking himself.

17:22.515 --> 17:27.216
He told me the people
who'd come today are his best friends.

17:27.355 --> 17:30.452
He said that you were busy
with work and didn't meet often.

17:30.476 --> 17:35.095
So, he wanted to prepare a meal
with the local fish for everyone today.

17:36.355 --> 17:37.615
This man is truly...

17:40.676 --> 17:42.412
- Alright.
- I'll leave you guys to chat.

17:42.436 --> 17:44.212
Let me know if you want
more oil tea. I gotta go.

17:44.236 --> 17:46.615
- Okay, thank you, madam.
- You're welcome.

17:47.875 --> 17:51.396
- How can you, Sheng?
- You're so tight-lipped.

17:51.396 --> 17:54.011
- That's right.
- You didn't even tell me.

17:54.035 --> 17:56.896
I'll go in to see if my help is needed.
Make yourselves at home.

17:57.676 --> 18:00.575
- She's feeling shy.
- She gets shy easily.

18:00.636 --> 18:03.612
Stop the noise. Does any of you feel

18:03.636 --> 18:06.571
something seems off
with those two today?

18:06.595 --> 18:10.531
Right. And we're sitting
at such a big table.

18:10.555 --> 18:14.732
- Doesn't it kind of resemble...?
- Resemble what?

18:14.756 --> 18:18.612
- You know that.
- A wedding party.

18:18.636 --> 18:21.172
- Exactly.
- Put on the suit for me.

18:21.196 --> 18:22.355
- Red envelopes!
- I didn't bring a red envelope.

18:22.355 --> 18:25.656
- I didn't bring cash.
- Transferring is fine.

18:45.476 --> 18:47.335
- It smells so good.
- Be careful.

18:49.636 --> 18:50.636
Come on.

18:53.676 --> 18:55.396
Hello, I'm Xiaoxing, Geng Xiaoxing.

18:55.396 --> 18:57.055
- Hello.
- Hello.

19:14.636 --> 19:16.251
- Another dish.
- This one is nice, too.

19:16.275 --> 19:18.436
- Another one.
- This is poached fish in chili oil.

19:18.436 --> 19:20.132
- Eat it.
- Really nice. Have a taste.

19:20.156 --> 19:22.196
- Here's another dish.
- This is so delicious.

19:22.196 --> 19:24.216
The Peacock Train Fish.

19:26.156 --> 19:27.696
Beautiful plating.

19:45.035 --> 19:48.055
- Cheers.
- It's a joyful reunion.

20:06.436 --> 20:08.896
Here it comes, the beer fish.

20:11.035 --> 20:14.212
Qiang Qingci,
you made our signature dish.

20:14.236 --> 20:16.412
How dare you make it
in front of us locals?

20:16.436 --> 20:17.996
Madam, come have a taste
and see how he did.

20:17.996 --> 20:19.236
Come to taste it.

20:19.236 --> 20:21.456
- I'm coming.
- This place setting is untouched.

20:21.956 --> 20:24.615
- Have a taste.
- Taste it.

20:28.835 --> 20:30.291
- Authentic.
- Not bad.

20:30.315 --> 20:33.811
- Qiang Qingci, did you hear that?
- Try this.

20:33.835 --> 20:35.636
- Taste it.
- Put it aside.

20:35.636 --> 20:37.375
What's coming now?

20:38.996 --> 20:41.095
The last dish.

20:41.996 --> 20:44.436
- Come on.
- This is our restaurant's signature dish.

20:44.436 --> 20:45.932
You can even make this.

20:45.956 --> 20:47.811
What if the chef in our restaurant
sees this tomorrow

20:47.835 --> 20:50.295
and decides to resign?
Will you work for me instead?

20:50.835 --> 20:52.416
- Be careful.
- The pot.

20:54.075 --> 20:56.236
Sheng ordered this dish for everyone

20:56.236 --> 20:58.775
when getting out of the car.

20:59.875 --> 21:03.212
The spotted fish hotpot. We had it
at this restaurant on our first visit.

21:03.236 --> 21:08.795
Right. Since we are
on this subject, let's start eating.

21:08.795 --> 21:11.491
Mr. Mo has been cooking
and hasn't eaten a little yet.

21:11.515 --> 21:14.956
- Let's toast him.
- Come on.

21:14.956 --> 21:16.835
- Thanks for your hard work.
- Cheers.

21:16.835 --> 21:19.345
First of all,
we should thank Mr. Mo for paying

21:19.345 --> 21:21.251
to take us on this nostalgic trip.

21:21.275 --> 21:24.896
Next, we need to say
some auspicious words.

21:25.595 --> 21:27.571
What should we say? Let's each say some.

21:27.595 --> 21:30.976
I'll go first. I'm not very eloquent,
so I'll say the easy ones.

21:32.156 --> 21:34.515
- May all go well.
- Don't embarrass us.

21:34.515 --> 21:38.295
- What's wrong?
- It should be for a couple.

21:38.396 --> 21:40.416
- May your love be solid.
- Right.

21:40.716 --> 21:41.916
- Isn't it good?
- This is good.

21:41.916 --> 21:45.251
- Good.
- Your words sound like...

21:45.275 --> 21:49.535
Actually, I think it really sounds like
we're at a wedding feast.

21:50.396 --> 21:53.132
Be casual. Sheng is shy.

21:53.156 --> 21:56.811
I'd like to say thank you.
Sheng and I graduated together today.

21:56.835 --> 21:59.855
Celebrating our graduation here
is just perfect.

22:01.236 --> 22:04.771
- You're welcome.
- Great! Thanks, Mr. Qiang.

22:04.795 --> 22:08.236
Perfect Voice for a perfect evening.

22:08.236 --> 22:11.412
- Is this your late-night radio show?
- Come on.

22:11.436 --> 22:14.932
Let's save whatever we have to say
for their real wedding, okay?

22:14.956 --> 22:17.496
I'll speak for everyone.
Then we'll start eating.

22:17.956 --> 22:22.835
- May we all never part ways.
- Well said.

22:22.835 --> 22:26.176
- Long live our friendship!
- Long live our friendship!

22:30.595 --> 22:32.452
Everyone, here are some condiments.

22:32.476 --> 22:34.531
Season to your own taste.
I'll leave you to it.

22:34.555 --> 22:37.115
- Okay.
- That kumquat is especially delicious.

22:37.115 --> 22:39.575
- I'll season it for you.
- Super delicious.

22:39.996 --> 22:42.476
- Help me season one.
- Help me with this, please.

22:42.476 --> 22:45.896
- Come with me.
- It's really tasty. You should try it.

22:46.035 --> 22:48.416
- Soy sauce.
- Soy sauce.

22:50.515 --> 22:52.976
You prepared
an extra portion separately?

22:55.436 --> 22:56.696
Let's eat alone.

23:00.835 --> 23:04.615
Is it nice if we eat here by ourselves?

23:12.636 --> 23:14.095
It is special today.

23:20.075 --> 23:22.216
- Is it tasty?
- Yes.

23:30.115 --> 23:31.571
- Come on.
- Eat the soup.

23:31.595 --> 23:35.335
- It's tasty.
- I'm tired of saying "tasty" tonight.

23:37.436 --> 23:40.531
Come on. Anyway,
it's Qiang Qingci's treat.

23:40.555 --> 23:43.916
- Don't stand on ceremony. Fill up.
- Others may think you're paying.

23:43.916 --> 23:46.136
- Don't just drink. Eat it.
- It's hot.

23:46.315 --> 23:48.656
