- Fine.

23:51.835 --> 23:53.136
Try this.

23:57.795 --> 23:59.416
Enough. So annoying.

24:00.835 --> 24:04.295
I have a question, Juemei.
I have been wondering

24:04.436 --> 24:06.692
when exactly you two started dating.

24:06.716 --> 24:10.936
Yeah, we tried to deduce the time
but just couldn't figure it out.

24:11.315 --> 24:14.132
At least tell us how you
formally confessed your feelings.

24:14.156 --> 24:15.736
- Yeah.
- Yeah.

24:20.875 --> 24:25.976
- Eat it.
- What? There wasn't a formal confession?

24:26.275 --> 24:29.095
- You were wrong, Zhou.
- Yes.

24:29.275 --> 24:31.445
Can you stop worrying about this?

24:31.445 --> 24:35.015
When it's meant to be,
you just end up together.

24:37.275 --> 24:41.612
Xiaoxing, sorry. He let you down
as a man from our dubbing team.

24:41.636 --> 24:45.172
But this is definitely not on us.

24:45.196 --> 24:48.515
- It's his problem alone.
- If it were me, I'd confess in person.

24:48.515 --> 24:51.652
- Do you even have a crush?
- Zhou's tall and big,

24:51.676 --> 24:54.732
- but he's shy and stubborn.
- Exactly.

24:54.756 --> 24:55.976
Watch your words.

24:57.396 --> 24:58.736
Right?

24:59.916 --> 25:02.855
I just love that he's shy and stubborn.

25:05.396 --> 25:08.335
- My goosebumps.
- Here's to being stubborn. I'll drink.

25:09.555 --> 25:11.055
Here's to a sharp tongue.

25:16.835 --> 25:19.575
- Where are you going, Doudou?
- I'm going out for some fresh air.

25:21.835 --> 25:23.811
- Eat it.
- Eat this soup.

25:23.835 --> 25:25.575
- It is nutritious.
- I'll try it.

25:35.688 --> 25:36.520
I just had a breakup.

25:36.520 --> 25:39.216
I can't bear to
listen to them talk about this.

25:40.156 --> 25:44.615
So are you by yourself or...?

25:44.676 --> 25:46.896
I have so many chefs and waiters here.

25:47.355 --> 25:50.936
You know how to chat. Cheers.

26:23.835 --> 26:25.535
When I first met you,

26:27.156 --> 26:28.855
I was a high school student,

26:30.555 --> 26:31.976
and you were in college.

26:33.436 --> 26:34.976
No matter how I thought,

26:36.996 --> 26:38.575
