26:50.996 --> 26:52.936
I could only act
like a high school student.

27:06.996 --> 27:08.375
I...

27:09.875 --> 27:11.256
Well...

27:14.795 --> 27:16.496
I don't know what to say.

27:17.595 --> 27:19.095
Or can you

27:21.275 --> 27:22.656
