29:05.275 --> 29:07.136
Do you remember the baked durian?

29:07.595 --> 29:09.775
Yes. You want to eat it again?

29:12.315 --> 29:13.315
Let's go.

29:14.515 --> 29:19.051
Baked durian.
Freshly baked durian in Yangshuo.

29:19.075 --> 29:21.315
