- Two servings of baked durian.

29:21.315 --> 29:24.615
Alright, would you also like
some durian ice cream? It's popular.

29:25.476 --> 29:26.972
- Okay, I'll have one.
- Alright.

29:26.996 --> 29:28.896
- How much is it in total?
- 35.

29:37.355 --> 29:41.132
The photo was taken two years ago
during the 10th anniversary

29:41.156 --> 29:44.412
