- Thank you.

30:18.396 --> 30:21.892
Tell your boss we love
her baked durian so much.

30:21.916 --> 30:24.095
It's been two years
and we still can't forget it.

30:24.196 --> 30:26.216
You watched the 10th anniversary, too?

30:28.315 --> 30:30.656
We really like the Perfect Voice Studio.

30:31.795 --> 30:35.256
- Alright then, take care.
- Okay. Let's go.

30:37.644 --> 30:41.788
(Qiang Qingci)

30:42.875 --> 30:44.815
