- Yes.

30:45.476 --> 30:49.172
Right, just now two people mentioned
they enjoyed our baked durian a lot.

30:49.196 --> 30:52.491
They like that dubbing team
just like you do.

30:52.515 --> 30:54.172
Really? Did you give them a discount?

30:54.196 --> 30:56.976
